  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Age from 18 to 80 years

          -  BMI&lt;35

          -  Presence of symptomatic diverticular disease

          -  ASA I-III

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  age &gt; 80 years

          -  BMI&gt;35

          -  ASA IV

          -  Hinchey III-IV

          -  Past performed procedure that could be modify the nervous pattern (i.e. colorectal
             surgery, left nephrectomy, hysteroannessectomy)
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
